race.comment: HE'S A COOL CAT (6) showed sharp improvement last start when only just missing the frame. With further progression expected and Pannell taking the reins from a good draw, he looks set to take plenty of stopping. ENUFF SEDUCTION (1) rattled home strongly to just miss here last time, beating a number of these rivals. Will be ridden quietly again and saved for the last crack. No reason he can't finish over the top. BEEN OUR ANGEL (2) was nailed late after leading throughout in the same race. Strips fitter now and will be hard to catch if allowed to dictate. ROUND TWO (3) is another likely leader and has the draw to advantage. He can give a bold sight and shouldn't be overlooked.
